<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>鸡祥富贵</title>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <!-- <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico"> -->
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="{$path_img}/images/activity/2017_March/activity01/mobile/index-mobile.css">
	<script src="{$path_js}/js/activity/2017_March/activity01/mb/flexible.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<input type="hidden" id="token" value="{$token}"/>

    <div class="header">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="logo" href="javascript:;">宝开彩票</a>
        <div class="chicken">
          <button class="btn-reward J-reward" type="button">领取红包</button>
          <div class="egg J-egg"></div>
        </div>
        <a href="phlotto://go_recharge" class="btn J-chongzhi">鸿运充值</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="activity-con">
          <h1 class="title">活动内容</h1>

          <div class="content">
            <p class="desc">活动时间内每日累计存款达到相应要求<br>流水达到充值金额一倍<br>即可获得相对应的奖金</p>

            <table class="table">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th>日累计充值</th>
                  <td>≥1,000</td>
                  <td>≥5,000</td>
                  <td>≥10,000</td>
                  <td>≥50,000</td>
                  <td>≥100,000</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th>普通用户奖金</th>
                  <td>6</td>
                  <td>32</td>
                  <td>68</td>
                  <td>388</td>
                  <td>888</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th>VIP用户奖金</th>
                  <td>8</td>
                  <td>38</td>
                  <td>88</td>
                  <td>488</td>
                  <td>1188</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th>流水需求</th>
                  <td colspan="5">充值金额的一倍流水</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="activity-rule">
          <h1 class="title">活动规则</h1>

          <div class="content">
            <ul>
              <li class="item">活动返奖，参与游戏只限于宝开彩票旗舰版平台彩票类游戏。投注必须为已开奖注单，视为有效投注。PT、大乐博、六合彩、骰宝大小单双销量不计算在活动销量内。</li>
              <li class="item">本次活动包含上下级充值。</li>
              <li class="item">超级2000玩法按实际投注额的80%进行结算。<br>如：用户超级2000玩法中投注额为1,000，则结算销量为1,000*80%=800。</li>
              <li class="item">奖金领取：满足活动要求后需要您在活动页面点击领取前一天的奖金，领取后系统自动派发到您的账号，届时请留意您的帐变信息；每日0点清空前一天可领取奖金。</li>
              <li class="item">平台新注册用户，首存优惠不得与本次活动同时享受。当首存优惠领取后，方可参与本次活动。</li>
              <li class="item">活动期间禁止任何作弊行为，一经发现平台将取消参与活动资格，严重者将被冻结账号处理。</li>
              <li class="item">宝开平台保留活动最终解释权。</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="container">©2003-2017 宝开彩票 All Rights Reserved</div>
    </div>

    <div class="hongbao J-hongbao">
      <div class="hongbao-body">
        <div class="up"></div>
        <div class="mid">
          <div class="bless"></div>
          <p><span class="price J-price">38888</span><i class="priceunit">元</i></p>
        </div>
        <div class="down">
          <button class="btn-confirm J-confirm" type='button'>确定</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pop J-pop">
      <div class="pop-body">
        <div class="pop-close J-pop-close"></div>
        <p class="tips J-tips">目前活动尚未开始！</p>
        <a class="btn-index J-btn" href="javascript:;"></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="{$path_js}/js/activity/2017_March/activity01/jquery-3.1.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="{$path_js}/js/activity/2017_March/activity01/frames.js"></script>
    <script src="{$path_js}/js/activity/2017_March/activity01/mb/index-mb.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
